<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>jīn rì nǐ yào zhī dào 迦南1400</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jīn rì nǐ yào zhī dào, yě yào láo jì zài xīn, tiān shàng de xià wéi yǒu yé hé huá tā shì shén,
 jīn rì nǐ yào zhī dào, yě yào láo jì zài xīn, tiān shàng de xià wéi yǒu yé hé huá tā shì shén,
 chú tā yǐ wài zài wú bié shén ā mén! chú tā yǐ wài zài wú bié shén ā mén! tā shì chuàng zào wàn yǒu de shén. shì dú yī zhēn shén!</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1400</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>